public static stringfalseNormalizer::normalize stringdizge intbiçimNormalizer::FORM_C
&style.procedural;
stringfalsenormalizer_normalize stringdizge intbiçimNormalizer::FORM_C
Belirtilen girdiyi normalleştirir ve dizge olarak döndürür.

  &reftitle.examples;

   - normalizer_normalize örneği


<?php
$char_A_ring = "\xC3\x85"; // 'å' (U+00C5)
$char_combining_ring_above = "\xCC\x8A";  // 'COMBINING RING ABOVE' (U+030A)

$char_1 = normalizer_normalize( $char_A_ring, Normalizer::FORM_C );
$char_2 = normalizer_normalize( 'A' . $char_combining_ring_above,
                                 Normalizer::FORM_C );

echo urlencode($char_1);
echo ' ';
echo urlencode($char_2);
?>




   - Nesne yönelimli örnek


